title: KGMU Notification 2026 - Walk-in interview for Project Technician/ Project Technical Support II Posts
description: The King George's Medical University (KGMU) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 01 Project Technician/ Project Technical Support II Jobs. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their 12th, DMLT, Diploma, or any degree can apply for the KGMU Notification 2026. The interested applicants can attend the walk-in interview.
